::Feline:;

She jumped as Rex turned the corner and suprized her. She dropped the 
rest of the supplies.  She stood there looking at the gun in his 
hand.  "I...ah..Iron Raptor told me to...ah..set up a repair bay in 
the CR chamber for her friends whom she will go out serching for."  
She backed away from him and stood against the wall.  "I...I was 
getting parts and...wires..incase they needed them in repairs." She 
was shaking slightly and showed fear on her 
face.  "It's.....for.....Dino...and..Trava..." She didn't take her 
eyes off his gun or him.  Her body was stiff and shaking.  She 
cringed away from him.
